在[[高爾夫球|高爾夫球]]運動中，'''一桿進洞'''（hole in one）是指自[[發球區|發球區]]開球後直接將球擊入目標球洞的情況。

一桿進洞通常發生在3[[標準桿|桿]]洞，這是標準高爾夫球場距離最短的洞。而4桿洞和5桿洞對大多數高爾夫球手來說都太長了，僅有少數擅長開球的選手能實現這一壯舉。戶外高爾夫開球需要精確的擊球和強大的力量，而一桿進洞更是需要[[運氣|幸運]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Halley|first1=Jim|title=With holes in one, no matter how you slice them luck is vital|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/golf/2006-07-16-hole-in-one_x.htm|newspaper=USA Today|access-date=2014-10-31|archive-date=2022-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212213111/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/golf/2006-07-16-hole-in-one_x.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Oscarson|first1=Paul|title=Top 10 Craziest Holes-in-One|url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1693444-top-10-craziest-holes-in-one|website=The Bleacher Report|access-date=2014-10-31|archive-date=2014-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224060502/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1693444-top-10-craziest-holes-in-one|dead-url=no}}</ref>。因此其它高爾夫競技中的精彩演出（如在5桿洞實現兩桿進洞的[[标准杆#双鹰球|信天翁]]）都不如一桿進洞能給觀眾留下深刻印象<ref>{{cite magazine |first=Bill |last=Fields |url=http://www.golfdigest.com/majors/masters/index.ssf?/majors/masters/gw20040402albatross.html |title=The Rarest Bird: The albatross took flight at the 1935 Masters, but golf's most unlikely shot isn't easy to find |magazine=Golf World |date=2004-04-02 |access-date=2013-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070305063301/http://www.golfdigest.com/majors/masters/index.ssf?%2Fmajors%2Fmasters%2Fgw20040402albatross.html |archive-date=2007-03-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==罕見度==
一桿進洞非常少見。雖然高技巧可以提高一桿進洞的可能性，然而好運在實現一桿進洞中有重要要素<ref name=odds>{{cite web |url=http://www.holeinoneinsurance.com/hole-in-one-odds.html |title=What Are The Odds of Making a Hole In One? |publisher=US Hole In One |access-date=2013-02-14 |archive-date=2012-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109172936/http://www.holeinoneinsurance.com/hole-in-one-odds.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。對實現一桿進洞的球手來說，在俱樂部酒吧請所有其他球手喝酒是傳統<ref>{{cite web |url=https://abcnews.go.com/blogs/headlines/2012/07/golfers-hit-hole-in-ones-within-seconds-of-each-other/ |title=Golfers Hit Hole-In-Ones Within Seconds of Each Other |publisher=ABC News |date=2012-07-19 |access-date=2013-12-07 |archive-date=2020-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111041952/https://abcnews.go.com/blogs/headlines/2012/07/golfers-hit-hole-in-ones-within-seconds-of-each-other/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]》雜誌曾報道在1922年，美國的高爾夫球製造了1,200次一桿進洞記錄<ref>{{cite magazine |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title=Miscellany |url=https://time.com/vault/issue/1923-03-03/page/27/ |magazine=Time |location=[[New_York_City|New York City]] |page=27 |date=1923-03-03 |access-date=2021-03-02 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306140359/http://time.com/vault/issue/1923-03-03/page/27/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在{{link-en|1973年英國高爾夫公開賽|1973 Open Championship}}上，{{link-en|吉恩·薩拉贊|Gene Sarazen}}曾以71歲的年齡打出一桿進洞。Earl Dietering在78歲時創出在一輪比賽內打出兩個一桿進洞，是迄今世界最高齡的一桿進洞記錄<ref>{{cite news |title=It's a pair of aces for senior golfer |newspaper=The Commercial Appeal |first=Phil |last=Stukenborg |date=April 20, 2012 |url=http://www.commercialappeal.com/news/2012/apr/20/its-a-pair-of-aces-for-senior-golfer/ |access-date=2013-02-14 |archive-date=2014-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502022515/http://www.commercialappeal.com/news/2012/apr/20/its-a-pair-of-aces-for-senior-golfer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在1971年於英格蘭皇家諾維奇高爾夫俱樂部舉辦的{{link-en|馬丁尼國際賽|Martini International}}上，{{link-en|約翰·哈德森 (高爾夫球手)|John Hudson (golfer)|約翰·哈德森}}實現連續兩洞打出一桿進洞的記錄。這也是大型職業賽事中唯一的連續實現一桿進洞的記錄<ref name=guinness>{{cite book |title=Golf: Records, Facts and Champions |url=https://archive.org/details/golfrecordsfacts0000stee |first=Donald |last=Steel |author-link=Donald Steel |publisher=Guinness Superlatives Ltd. |year=1987 |isbn=0-85112-847-5 |page=[https://archive.org/details/golfrecordsfacts0000stee/page/222 222]}}</ref><ref name=alliss>{{cite book |title=The Who's Who of Golf |url=https://archive.org/details/whoswhoofgolf0000alli |first=Peter |last=Alliss |author-link=Peter Alliss |publisher=Orbis Publishing |year=1983 |isbn=0-85613-520-8 |page=[https://archive.org/details/whoswhoofgolf0000alli/page/250 250]}}</ref>。

雖然一桿進洞十分罕見，但在[[萊德盃|萊德盃]]上已有過6次一桿進洞記錄。第一次是在{{link-en|1973年萊德盃|1973 Ryder Cup}}，由{{link-en|彼得·巴特勒 (高爾夫球手)|Peter Butler (golfer)|彼得·巴特勒}}實現。20年之後，[[尼克·佛度|尼克·佛度]]在{{link-en|1993年萊德盃|1993 Ryder Cup}}成為第二位實現這一壯舉的球手。此後{{link-en|科斯坦蒂諾·羅卡|Costantino Rocca}}和{{link-en|霍華德·克拉克 (高爾夫球手)|Howard Clark|霍華德·克拉克}}在1995年打出一桿進洞，[[保羅·凱西|保羅·凱西]]和[[史考特·佛普蘭克|史考特·佛普蘭克]]在2006年打出一桿進洞<ref>{{cite news |title=6 Ryder Cup Hole In Ones |url=http://www.mdhio.net/6-ryder-cup-hole-in-ones/ |access-date=2014-10-01 |archive-date=2016-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330080621/http://www.mdhio.net/6-ryder-cup-hole-in-ones/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年8月11日，[[賈斯汀·羅斯|賈斯汀·羅斯]]在[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會高爾夫比賽|2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會高爾夫比賽]]上實現奧運會歷史上第一個一桿進洞<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.golfdigest.com/story/justin-rose-makes-the-first-hole-in-one-in-olympics-golf-history|title=Justin Rose makes the first hole-in-one in Olympics golf history - Golf Digest|last=Myers|first=Alex|access-date=2016-08-12|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029234207/https://www.golfdigest.com/story/justin-rose-makes-the-first-hole-in-one-in-olympics-golf-history|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==獎品==
一些職業賽事會為實現一桿進洞的球手提供獎品，大多是新車或和新車價值相近的現金（有時可達約400萬美元）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bizjournals.com/memphis/stories/2006/02/27/focus2.html |title=Hole-in-one insurance policies provide safety net for glitzy tournament contests |first=Chris |last=Harris |date=2006-02-26 |access-date=2013-02-14 |archive-date=2019-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213003932/https://www.bizjournals.com/memphis/stories/2006/02/27/focus2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這些高額獎金大多由保險公司支付。據精算師的計算，一位普通球手打出一桿進洞的機率是12,500分之1，職業球手是2,500分之1<ref name=odds/>。

==5桿洞的一桿進洞==
截止2018年，僅有4次在5桿洞實現一桿進洞的記錄<ref name=Condor01>{{cite web|title=Golf A to Z - The 'Condor'|url=https://golftoday.co.uk/golf-a-to-z-the-condor/|accessdate=2021-04-03|work=Golf Today|dead-url=no|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224185515/https://golftoday.co.uk/golf-a-to-z-the-condor/}}</ref><ref name=Condor02>{{cite web|title=Has There Ever Been a Hole-in-One on a Par-5 Hole?|url=http://golf.about.com/od/faqs/f/par5aces.htm|first=Brent|last=Kelley|publisher=About.com Golf|access-date=2014-08-24|archive-date=2017-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214061853/http://golf.about.com/od/faqs/f/par5aces.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pga.com/news/golf-buzz/odds-hole-in-one-albatross-condor|title=Odds for hole in one, albatross, condor|website=www.pga.com|access-date=2019-08-23|archive-date=2019-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823203536/https://www.pga.com/news/golf-buzz/odds-hole-in-one-albatross-condor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曾有球手用3號鐵桿在馬蹄形5桿洞實現一桿進洞<ref name=Condor01/><ref name=Condor02/>。最長距離的5桿洞一桿進洞記錄是{{convert|517|yd|m|0|disp=or}}，於2002年在[[丹佛|丹佛]]的綠谷牧場高爾夫俱樂部實現。高海拔的稀薄空氣令這次壯舉得以實現<ref name=Condor01/><ref name=Condor02/>。在職業賽事中，還沒有一次5桿洞的一桿進洞記錄<ref name=Condor01/>。

